Title: S5 Ep. 220 Ryan Estes
Description:
Ryan Estes  shared four words that describe him and they would make a GREAT book title. Ryan's four words are Chop wood, carry water! Listen to the show to hear what it means. His founder story includes starting two businesses Kit Caster and Go Wild Cast.  On the second half of the show we talk about robots, aliens, and ethical dilemmas of AI.
